## Usage

### Routes

- **GET /users**: Get all users.
- **GET /users/:id**: Get user by ID.

### Example

To get all users, send a GET request to `http://localhost:3000/users`.

To get a specific user with ID 1, send a GET request to `http://localhost:3000/users/1`.

